- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Runtime/Core/IIpcOutboundChannel.cs
    Pure C# port that abstracts the byte-level send path so CoreIpcBus
    stays Unity- and transport-agnostic. Exposes:
        - bool IsConnected { get; }
        - ValueTask SendAsync(ReadOnlyMemory<byte> bytes, CancellationToken ct)
    Concrete adapters (WebSocket, InMemoryLoopback) implement this in
    later tasks (4.x / 5.1) and the runtime composition (task 7.1)
    wires it up. Tests inject a fake implementation to drive the bus.
